# UI & Assets Standards

## 1. UI Stack
- Framework: **Unity UI Canvas (UGUI)**.
- Text: Use **TextMeshPro (TMP)** for all UI text. No legacy Text components.

## 2. Asset Management
- Standard: **Addressables** is mandatory for runtime loading.
- Exceptions: `Resources.Load` permitted **ONLY** for `Assets/Resources/Data/*`.
